OL,7,FA new mobile alert system is to be
OL,8,Ftested that will sound an alarm on
OL,9,Fpeople's phones warning them of
OL,10,Fimminent danger .
OL,12,FA UK-wide trial of the new government
OL,13,Fsystem will take place on 23 April,
OL,14,Fwhen everyone in the country will
OL,15,Freceive a test alert on their mobile
OL,16,Fphones.
OL,18,FThe Government says the technology will
OL,19,Fallow more effective response efforts
OL,20,Fto public emergencies such as flooding
OL,21,Fand wildfires.
OL,3,CHow emergency alerts will work as UK
OL,4,Ctests new system to push warning
OL,5,Cmessages to everyone
